ğŸš€ Running the Application
â–¶ï¸ Start FastAPI backend
python -m uvicorn app:app --reload

Backend runs at:
http://127.0.0.1:8000

Swagger API docs:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

Start Streamlit UI (new terminal)
